<sect1 id="dir_04e46b302a6aadc7f23a11997ed7852b_1autotoc_md392">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::timing</title><para>Game timer management system.</para>
<para>This module provides timers, commands, components, and systems for tracking elapsed time, controlling timer state transitions, and observing timer updates from within the ECS.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_04e46b302a6aadc7f23a11997ed7852b_1autotoc_md393">
<title>Submodules</title><para><table rows="5" cols="2"><row>
