</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>types/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Core type definitions (<computeroutput>TimerState</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>TimerRevision</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>TimerControlContext</computeroutput>)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
